NK016(ma)013:0: na rag dong sprugs kyi dbang gi cho ga mtshams
NK016(ma)013:1: sbyor gyis brgyan pa bde chen lam bzang zhes bya
NK016(ma)013:2: ba bzhugs so // na rag dong sprug rnal 'byor
NK016(ma)013:3: spyi khrus chen po'i dbang gi mtshams sbyor bde chen
NK016(ma)013:5: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)013:6: rigs brgya'i khyab bdag dpal ldan rdo rje sems //
NK016(ma)013:7: rab 'byams zhi dang khro bo'i phrin las kyis //
NK016(ma)013:8: srid zhi kun la dbang bsgyur 'khor lo'i mgon //
NK016(ma)013:9: mnyam med gter chen bla mar phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)013:10: mkha' mnyam 'gro la tshad med thugs rje yis //
NK016(ma)013:11: ma rig dug lnga'i snying bo kun bcom nas //
NK016(ma)013:12: srid mtsho 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las bsgral te //
NK016(ma)013:13: rnam grol sku bzhir smin mdzad ded dpon mchog /
NK016(ma)013:14: gang thugs ye shes gcig nyid sgyu 'phrul gyis //
NK016(ma)013:16: go 'phang mngon du byed pa'i thabs kyi sgo //
NK016(ma)013:17: dbang gi mtshams sbyor bde chen lam bzang bshad //
NK016(ma)013:18: de yang rten gyi gang zag rang gzhan gyis bsdus
NK016(ma)013:19: pa'i sems can thams cad sgrib gnyis sbyong zhing tshogs
NK016(ma)013:20: gnyis phul du byung ba dang dngos grub kyi skal
NK016(ma)013:22: thar 'dod rnams kyi lam 'dir 'jug par bya'o //
NK016(ma)013:27: gang du bya ba'i gnas khang nyid byi dor legs par byas la /
NK016(ma)013:28: der rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor cho ga bzhin du
NK016(ma)013:29: bzhengs pa'am ras bris kyi dkyil 'khor bkram pa gang
NK016(ma)013:30: rung bya / rnam rgyal bum pa dang las bum
NK016(ma)013:31: gnyis kha rgyan mgul chings nang bcud sogs spyi dang
NK016(ma)013:32: mthun par bshams pa'i rnam bum dkyil 'khor gyi dbus
NK016(ma)013:33: su many+dzi'i steng du bkod pa'i khar sku tsaka dang
NK016(ma)013:34: rung bya / gzungs rdor bzhag / dkyil 'khor gyi mdun lta bur sman gtor rak+ta dang /
NK016(ma)013:35: de'i phyi rim la bdug spos /
NK016(ma)013:38: dri chab rnams lha grangs dang mnyam pa sogs ci tsam 'byor pa bshams /
NK016(ma)013:39: gzhan yang tshogs kyi yo byad /
NK016(ma)013:42: dar 'phan rgyal mtshan sogs kyis khor yug thams cad mdzes par brgyan cing /
NK016(ma)013:43: slob dpon gyi mdun du nang mchod /
NK016(ma)013:53: me tog man+dala gyi ra ba /
NK016(ma)013:56: man+dala sogs 'og tu dgos pa'i yo byad rnams phyag
NK016(ma)013:57: bzhes mthong brgyud bzhin ma tshang ba med par 'du
NK016(ma)013:58: bya'o // gnyis pa dngos gzhi la /
NK016(ma)013:59: sgrub mchod dang dbang gi cho ga gnyis las /
NK016(ma)013:61: rjes bla mas mdzad pa'i cho ga 'khor pa kun sgrol ltar bya'o //
NK016(ma)013:62: gnyis pa dbang gi cho ga la /
NK016(ma)013:64: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK016(ma)013:65: de nas slob ma 'jug par bya //
NK016(ma)013:66: zhes gsung pa ltar slob dpon rang nyid 'jug pa dang /
NK016(ma)013:67: slob ma 'jug pa'i chos gnyis las /
NK016(ma)013:68: dang po slob dpon rang nyid slob ma 'jug pa ltar dkyil 'khor du zhugs te /
NK016(ma)013:69: bdag 'jug gi tshul du dbang rdzogs par len pa'ang /
NK016(ma)013:70: mi nus na dkyil gyi shar sgor gus bas 'dug ste /
NK016(ma)013:71: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang dbyer med du bsgoms nas rig pa'i me tog dor la /
NK016(ma)013:74: h+aum badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK016(ma)013:75: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK016(ma)013:76: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa /
NK016(ma)013:78: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum /
NK016(ma)013:80: dam tshig pa dang ye shes pa gnyis kyi sku
NK016(ma)013:81: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rnams gnyis su med
NK016(ma)013:82: par bsam nas // ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK016(ma)013:83: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK016(ma)013:84: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK016(ma)013:85: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK016(ma)013:89: badz+ra sa ma ya hoh zhes dngos grub bskul zhing bstim pa'o //
NK016(ma)013:90: gnyis pa slob ma gzhug par bzod gsol gnang ba zhu ba ni /
NK016(ma)013:91: dkyil 'khor la thal mo sbyar bas btud de //
NK016(ma)013:92: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i //
NK016(ma)013:93: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK016(ma)013:96: zhes gsol ba btab pas gnang ba sbyin par bsam /
NK016(ma)013:97: de ltar legs par tshar nas dkyil 'khor yol bas sgrib la 'jog go //
NK016(ma)013:98: gnyis pa dngos gzhi dbang bskur ba la /
NK016(ma)013:100: dang po 'jug pa la'ang dgu las /
NK016(ma)013:102: slob ma rnams dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol du ji
NK016(ma)013:103: ltar bltams pa sogs kyis las bum gyi chus khrus
NK016(ma)013:104: bya zhing / de nas phyag byas la gral du 'khod pa dang /
NK016(ma)013:105: sngon gtor ma h+aa kro d+h+ais bsang /
NK016(ma)013:107: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i snod
NK016(ma)013:108: yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du gtor ma kha
NK016(ma)013:109: dog dri ro nus pa phun sum tshogs par bsam
NK016(ma)013:111: sarba b+hu ta a kar+sha ya dzahs mgron rnams bkug /
NK016(ma)013:112: sarba big+n+aana sogs kyi bsngosa la /
NK016(ma)013:114: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)013:115: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)013:116: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK016(ma)013:117: chos can rgyu 'bras sogs kyi bden ston sngon du 'gro ba'i mthar /
NK016(ma)013:118: h'u h'u h'u bi shwa sogs kyi drag sngags bzla
NK016(ma)013:119: zhing thun gyi brabs te spos rol dang bcas tsham
NK016(ma)013:120: rngams kyis bgegs rnams phyir bskrad par bsam /
NK016(ma)013:121: de nas badz+ra rak+sha rak+sha h+aum zhes brjod pas /
NK016(ma)013:122: steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad rdo rje bsrung ba'i
NK016(ma)013:123: ra ba d+r+wa ba gur bla bres ye shes kyi
NK016(ma)013:124: me dpung / dus mtha'i rlung nag rgya mtsho'i rba
NK016(ma)013:125: rlabs 'khrug pa'i ra ba gsum rim gyis phyogs kun
NK016(ma)013:126: khyab pas mtshams bcad par bsam la srung 'khor gsal
NK016(ma)013:127: me dpung / gdab / de nas las kyi rdo rje me tog bkram bsdu bya zhing /
NK016(ma)013:129: 'o nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad
NK016(ma)013:130: kyi don du bla na med pa yang dag par
NK016(ma)013:131: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang rin po che
NK016(ma)013:132: sku tshe 'di nyid la thob par bya /
NK016(ma)013:133: de ma thob kyi bar du yang lam sgrub pa'i
NK016(ma)013:134: 'gal rkyen bar gcod kyi rtsa ba sdig pa dang
NK016(ma)013:135: dam tshig nyams chag rnams kyi gnyen por dpal rdo
NK016(ma)013:136: rje sems dpa' rigs brgya'i dkyil 'khor chen por rnal
NK016(ma)013:137: 'byor spyi'i nyams chag skong ba'i thabs phul du byung
NK016(ma)013:138: ba na rag dong sprugs kyi dbang zab mo zhu
NK016(ma)013:139: snyam pa'i byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed pa
NK016(ma)013:140: dang / chos gsan pa'i kun tu spyod pa'ang /
NK016(ma)013:143: dul ba'i dpal ni rnam par bskyed //
NK016(ma)013:144: dga' dang ldan pa'i mig gis blta //
NK016(ma)013:145: tshig gi bdud rtsi 'thung ba bzhin //
NK016(ma)013:146: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar dge ba'i gshes gnyen la
NK016(ma)013:147: dad gus dang ldan pas kun tu spyod pa bag
NK016(ma)013:148: dang ldan pa'i sgo nas gsan par zhu 'tshal /
NK016(ma)013:149: de la 'o skol gyi ston pa mnyam med yang
NK016(ma)013:150: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thabs mkhas la thugs
NK016(ma)013:151: rje chen po mnga' ba de nyid kyis gdul bya
NK016(ma)013:154: skal ba'i khyad par dang rjes su mthun par chos
NK016(ma)013:155: kyi bdud rtsi bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig bstan
NK016(ma)013:156: par mdzad pa rnams kyang nyon mongs pa'i gnyen po
NK016(ma)013:157: la dgongs te chos kyi phung po brgyad khri bzhi
NK016(ma)013:158: stong dang blo'i rim pa la dgongs te theg pa'i
NK016(ma)013:159: rim pa dgur bsdus te gsungs pa las /
NK016(ma)013:160: theg pa de yang bsdu na theg pa che chung gnyis sam /
NK016(ma)013:162: theg pa rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK016(ma)013:163: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa dang //
NK016(ma)013:165: zhes rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis su 'dus par gsungs pa las /
NK016(ma)013:166: da res 'dir rgyu pha rol tu phyin pa'i theg
NK016(ma)013:167: pa las khyad par du 'phags pa 'bras bu rdo
NK016(ma)013:169: de la yang phyi rgyud nang rgyud gnyis las 'dir nang rgyud /
NK016(ma)013:170: de'ang gangs can gyi ljongs 'dir gsang sngags gsar rnying gnyis su grags pa las /
NK016(ma)013:171: 'dir gsar ma las che ba drug gis khyad par du 'phags pa gsang sngags rnying ma /
NK016(ma)013:172: de la yang ring brgyud bka' ma /
NK016(ma)013:174: zam mo dag snang ste skor tsho gsum las 'dir bka' ma yin /
NK016(ma)013:175: de la rgyud sde dang sgrub sde gnyis las rgyud sde /
NK016(ma)013:176: de la'ang rgyud ma h+aa yo ga /
NK016(ma)013:178: man ngag a ti yo ga ste gsum las /
NK016(ma)013:179: 'di nyid a nu yo ga'i nang nas bskyed rdzogs
NK016(ma)013:180: rnam pa gsum gyis sgor zhugs pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK016(ma)013:181: rnams kyi nyams chag skong zhing rtog sgrib sbyong ba
NK016(ma)013:182: dang / sems can thams cad ngan song gi sdug
NK016(ma)013:183: bsngal las drangs nas bla na med pa'i dngos grub
NK016(ma)013:184: kyi skal ba can du byed pa'i thabs mchog rmad
NK016(ma)013:185: du byung ba rnal 'byor spyi khrus na rag dong
NK016(ma)013:186: sprugs mtshams med lnga sbyong gi dkyil 'khor chen por
NK016(ma)013:187: dbang bskur ba skabs su babs pa yin /
NK016(ma)013:188: de la yang rgyud dang man ngag so so'i dgongs
NK016(ma)013:189: pa la slob dpon so so'i bzhed pa'i dbang gis
NK016(ma)013:190: bzhi ste / 'di ltar glang po che rab 'bogs
NK016(ma)013:191: kyi rtogs pa gcig khol du phyungs pa kalpa dum
NK016(ma)013:192: bu'i rgyud dam bshags pa'i rgyud kyi le'u gsum pa
NK016(ma)013:193: gu rus mdzad pa'i gdams ngag gi las tho sogs
NK016(ma)013:194: kyis bkral ba zhi khro khrom dkrugs su grags pa
NK016(ma)013:195: bzhi ste / dang / gu rus mdzad pa'i sgrub
NK016(ma)013:196: thabs rgya zhang khrom gyi gter ma'i rjes su 'brangs
NK016(ma)013:197: te bshags rgyud du zhi khro'i le'u gsungs tshul gyi
NK016(ma)013:198: go rim bzhin du sgrub pa zhi khro gnas bsgyur
NK016(ma)013:199: bzhi ste / dang / dang / yi ge brgya
NK016(ma)013:200: pa dbang mchog rgyal po'i rgyud la brten pa zhi
NK016(ma)013:201: khro rigs bsdus sam pad+ma brgya ldan dang /
NK016(ma)013:202: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro sogs rang gzhung la bkol rgyud
NK016(ma)013:203: 'di nyid kyi kha bskang ba zhi khro rab 'byams
NK016(ma)013:205: 'dir zhi khro khrom dkrugs kyi lugs te /
NK016(ma)013:206: de yang 'gyod tshangs kyi rgyal po 'di nyid ji
NK016(ma)013:207: ltar byung ba'i khungs dang gleng bzhi'i dbang du bgyis
NK016(ma)013:208: na / sngon 'dod khams kyi gnas 'di na bram
NK016(ma)013:209: ze dung gi phreng ba can zhes bya ba rig
NK016(ma)013:210: pa'i gnas lnga la byang ba zhig la slob ma
NK016(ma)013:211: rgyal po'i bu zhig yod pa des slob sbyong rnams
NK016(ma)013:212: mthar phyin pa na da ni nga'i gong na rig
NK016(ma)013:213: par smra ba slob dpon 'di tsam du zad pas
NK016(ma)013:214: na / / 'di nyid gong du mi gtong snyam
NK016(ma)013:215: du bsam nas slob dpon la mi 'tshams pa'i las
NK016(ma)013:216: rngams po ches tho brtsams shing /
NK016(ma)013:217: slob dpon gyis kyang rang gi slob ma rgyal po'i
NK016(ma)013:218: phru gu des phrag dog gi sbyor ba byas par
NK016(ma)013:219: shes te zhe sdang gis dmod bor bas las des
NK016(ma)013:220: gnyis ka ngan song du ltung nas sdug bsngal drag
NK016(ma)013:221: pos nyam thag par gyur to //
NK016(ma)013:222: de'i tshe rgyal ba rnams kyi de nyid 'dul ba'i dus la bab par dgongs te /
NK016(ma)013:223: kun tu bzang po'i byin rlabs las dpal rdo rje
NK016(ma)013:224: sems dpar sprul nas de la 'gyod tshangs kyi bshags
NK016(ma)013:225: pa dang yi ge brgya pa'i sngags bstan pas sngon
NK016(ma)013:227: rnam smin dran te 'gyod pa drag po skyes pa la /
NK016(ma)013:228: rnam par snang mdzad kyi byin rlabs kyis bcom 'das
NK016(ma)013:229: gsang ba'i bdag po mngon par sprul nas phyi nang
NK016(ma)013:231: bram ze dang rgyal bu de'i byang chub kyi myu
NK016(ma)013:232: gu sngo skams su gyur pa slar yang gsos nas
NK016(ma)013:233: kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems dang 'phrad de 'bad
NK016(ma)013:234: bas rig 'dzin gyi sa la rim gyis gnas par
NK016(ma)013:235: gyur to // de lta bu'i nyams chag sbyong ba'i
NK016(ma)013:236: thabs phul du byung ba 'di nyid mi'i yul du
NK016(ma)013:237: ji ltar dar ba'i tshul yang /
NK016(ma)013:238: thub pa'i dbang po mya ngan las 'das nas lo
NK016(ma)013:239: nyi shu rtsa brgyad na gsang bdag gis ri ma
NK016(ma)013:240: la ya'i rtser rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga la chos
NK016(ma)013:241: 'khor bskor ba'i byin rlabs kyis rgyal po dzahl rmi
NK016(ma)013:242: ltas bdun mngon du snang ba las dngos su pusti
NK016(ma)013:243: glegs bam gyi char babs so //
NK016(ma)013:244: de'i nang nas glang po che rab 'bogs kyi le'u
NK016(ma)013:245: khol du phyung ba kalpa dum bu'i rgyud 'di nyid
NK016(ma)013:246: rgyal po dzahs ku ku r+aa dza la bshad /
NK016(ma)013:247: de nas rim par h+aum k+aa ra /
NK016(ma)013:252: bi ma la mi tra sogs kyis rgya gar gyi yul du dar bar mdzad /
NK016(ma)013:253: de nas bod yul 'dir bi ma la mi tras dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa la gsungs /
NK016(ma)013:254: de nas rim par sog po lha dpal /
NK016(ma)013:257: zhu ston gzhon nu snying po /
NK016(ma)013:260: zur chung shes rab grags pa /
NK016(ma)013:261: gsang bdag sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ge nas rig
NK016(ma)013:262: 'dzin phrin las lhun grub kyi bar du brgyud de
NK016(ma)013:263: gter chen bla ma la bka' babs pa dang /
NK016(ma)013:264: yang na bi ma la nas nyang ting 'dzin bzang po /
NK016(ma)013:265: de nas sbas blo gros dbang phyug sogs snying tig brgyud pa ltar ram /
NK016(ma)013:266: yang na bi ma las me long rdo rje la
NK016(ma)013:267: gsungs pa'i nye brgyud rmad du byung ba ste 'di
NK016(ma)013:268: dag ni brgyud pa'i lo rgyus kyi dbang du byas
NK016(ma)013:269: pa'o // de las byung ba'i gdams pa la'ang rtog
NK016(ma)013:270: tshogs lha'i rang bzhin du gdod ma nas rnam par
NK016(ma)013:271: dag pa'i bsgrub gzhi nyid dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)013:272: du gsal btab pa mkha' khyab 'bras bu ye shes
NK016(ma)013:273: kyi dkyil 'khor dang dbyer med du byed pa'i thabs
NK016(ma)013:274: la brten nas nang phung po rten gyi bshags pa
NK016(ma)013:275: pa'o // dang / phyag gi bkol byang la brten nas smre 'gyod tshig gi bshags dang /
NK016(ma)013:276: skong chen bzhi dag gyur tshogs mchod dang bcas pa'i phyi yo byad tshogs kyi bshags pa dang /
NK016(ma)013:277: bdag 'jug dang 'brel bar mkha' 'gro ma gtor ma'i
NK016(ma)013:278: dbang dang rig pa'i rtsal dbang brten nas gsang ba
NK016(ma)013:279: byang chub sems kyi bshags pa ste /
NK016(ma)013:280: de ltar bshags pa'i thabs rmad du byung ba rnam pa bzhi dang /
NK016(ma)013:281: de thams cad thun mong du 'grub par byed pa'i
NK016(ma)013:282: rig sngags lha so so'i bzlas pas thugs rgyud bskul
NK016(ma)013:283: nas / las sbyor dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi
NK016(ma)013:284: thugs rje'i 'od zer spro bsdu dang sbyar te yi
NK016(ma)013:285: ge brgya pa'i sham bur ngan song sbyong ba'i las
NK016(ma)013:286: sngags btags pa bzlas pas sdig sgrib sbyong ba rnams
NK016(ma)013:287: kyi thabs mchog phul du byung ba dang /
NK016(ma)013:288: dbang bskur ba'i rim pa gnyis su yod pa las /
NK016(ma)013:289: 'dir dbang bskur ba de skabs su babs pa yin /
NK016(ma)013:292: rdo rje 'chang gis gsungs pa ste //
NK016(ma)013:293: zhes pas dbang bskur ba de yang dkyil 'khor sngon du 'gro ba can yin /
NK016(ma)013:294: de la dkyil 'khor kyi ngo bo ni /
NK016(ma)013:296: gnas skabs bdun du snying po len //
NK016(ma)013:297: bkod pa gang rdzogs de ngo bo //
NK016(ma)013:298: zhes pas 'akoda pa lha'i 'khor lor rdzogs par snang ba'o //
NK016(ma)013:300: man+da la'i sgra las snying po 'dzin pa'am snying po len pa'i don dang /
NK016(ma)013:301: yang na zlum po'ang bskor ba'i don gyis dkyil 'khor zhes bya /
NK016(ma)013:302: dbye na skabs 'dir rgyas pa las /
NK016(ma)013:304: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan gsum //
NK016(ma)013:306: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK016(ma)013:307: zhes bdun du gsungs pa las /
NK016(ma)013:308: 'dir 'jug bya'i dkyil 'khor ni lhag pa gzugs brnyan
NK016(ma)013:309: gyi dkyil 'khor nyid sgrub pa skabs su babs pa
NK016(ma)013:310: yin / de la'ang slob dpon gyi bgyi 'os dang /
NK016(ma)013:312: slob dpon gyi bgyi 'os ni thun mong dang khyad
NK016(ma)013:313: par gyi sngon 'gros rgyud sbyang zhing tshogs bsags pa
NK016(ma)013:315: sbyang gzhi khams bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po gnyug
NK016(ma)013:316: ma mi shigs pa'i rdo rje gsum gyi ngo bor
NK016(ma)013:317: gnas pa dang / sbyang bya gnas lugs kyi rang
NK016(ma)013:318: ngo ma shes pas bdag dang bdag gir 'dzin pa'i
NK016(ma)013:320: sbyong byed bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gi lam rim pa
NK016(ma)013:321: gnyis kyis spyod pa'i thabs lha sngags ye shes ting
NK016(ma)013:323: de yang 'dir bdag mdun tha mi dad gyi tshul
NK016(ma)013:324: du thog mar ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis khog dbub
NK016(ma)013:325: pa / 'bras bu rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK016(ma)013:326: de la dbang bskur zhing byin gyis rlob pa /
NK016(ma)013:327: ye shes kyi 'khor lo spyan drang zhing bstim pa /
NK016(ma)013:328: thugs ka nas phye ba'i lhas 'phrul dag'i tshul gyis
NK016(ma)013:329: phyag dang mchod bstod sogs las kyi rim pas mnyes
NK016(ma)013:330: pa sgrub pa / dzapa khang phye nas bzlas pas thugs rgyud bskul ba /
NK016(ma)013:331: dbang don du bum pa sgrub pa /
NK016(ma)013:332: slob dpon rang nyid lha la dbang mi za ba'i
NK016(ma)013:333: phyir bdag don du dbang blang zhig gzhan don slob
NK016(ma)013:334: ma 'jug par bzod gsol gnang ba zhu ba dang
NK016(ma)013:335: bcas pa rnams bla ma dam pa'i phyag bzhes las
NK016(ma)013:336: ji ltar byung ba bzhin chad lhag med par gong
NK016(ma)013:337: du song grub / da khyed rang slob ma rnams
NK016(ma)013:338: kyi ngo skal du gyur pa la lha dang skal
NK016(ma)013:339: ba mnyam pa'i ched du dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i
NK016(ma)013:340: du song grub / chos dang / nugs nas dbang nod pa'i bya ba gnyis las /
NK016(ma)013:341: 'dir 'jug pa'i bya ba khrus dang bgegs bsal ba sngon du song nas /
NK016(ma)013:342: da bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo tha
NK016(ma)013:343: mi dad pa la dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i chos
NK016(ma)013:344: rnams zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul mdzod /
NK016(ma)013:346: de nas dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa'i phyir chas su gzhug pa ni /
NK016(ma)013:347: sngon chad gnyis 'dzin gyi zhen rtog 'thug pos mig
NK016(ma)013:348: ldongs pas dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs ma mjal ba'am
NK016(ma)013:349: / mjal na'ang dkyil 'khor so ma 'di nyid ma
NK016(ma)013:350: mjal mtshon byed du ras dmar po res gdong g.yogs
NK016(ma)013:353: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang mjal ba'i tshe
NK016(ma)013:354: phyag stong du mjal mi rung bas phyag tu u
NK016(ma)013:355: dum wa ra'i me tog gi phreng ba kha dog
NK016(ma)013:356: lnga pa re ba'i mos pa mdzod /
NK016(ma)013:357: ces +aa kh+aam w+ai ra h+aum gis me tog gtad /
NK016(ma)013:358: gnyis pa gsol ba gdab pa'i slad du dmigs pa 'di bzhin du mdzod /
NK016(ma)013:359: de yang sa phyogs 'di nyid dag pa rab 'byams
NK016(ma)013:360: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor chen por gyur pa'i nang
NK016(ma)013:361: du gang la dbang zhu ba'i yul du gyur pa'i
NK016(ma)013:362: slob dpon nyid kyang rigs dang dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i
NK016(ma)013:363: khyab bdag bcos ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa'
NK016(ma)013:364: dngos yin snyam pa'i mi phyed dad pa'i gdung shugs
NK016(ma)013:365: drag pos snyim pa te me tog dang bcas te
NK016(ma)013:366: thal mo sbyar nas gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rjes
NK016(ma)013:367: zlos mdzod / kye ma kyi hud rdo rje 'dzin //
NK016(ma)013:368: 'gro mgon thugs rjes bdag skyobs shig /
NK016(ma)013:369: dbang mchog rgyal bo bsgrag tu gsol //
NK016(ma)013:370: slad nas mi 'chab mi sbed do //
NK016(ma)013:372: gsum pa gnang ba sbyin pa ni /
NK016(ma)013:373: de ltar skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyed rnams
NK016(ma)013:374: kyis gsol ba btab par gyur pa la 'dod don
NK016(ma)013:375: gnang ba sbyin pa 'di la gsan pas khyab par
NK016(ma)013:376: gda' / bu 'dir shog cig rigs kyi bu //
NK016(ma)013:377: rang gi nyams dang zlas nyams kyis //
NK016(ma)013:378: na rag gnas su ltung ba las //
NK016(ma)013:379: skyob phyir dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK016(ma)013:381: de ltar slob bu las kyi rdo rjes dkyil 'khor
NK016(ma)013:382: gyi nang du drangs par mos su 'jug cing yol
NK016(ma)013:383: ba bsal / bzhi pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)013:384: de nas bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo
NK016(ma)013:385: dbyer ma mchis pa'i spyan sngar nyes byas kyi sdig
NK016(ma)013:386: ltung rnams bshags sdoms kyi bsam pas thal mo sbyar
NK016(ma)013:388: kye ma kye hud bdag 'dra bas //
NK016(ma)013:389: las ngan rnam smin myong 'gyur na //
NK016(ma)013:390: nyes byas 'gyod pas mthol lo bshags //
NK016(ma)013:391: mgon po'i thugs rjes bdag sgrol cig /
NK016(ma)013:393: lnga pa sems bskyed pa la gnyis las /
NK016(ma)013:394: dang po kun rdzob sems bskyed ni /
NK016(ma)013:395: 'di ltar mkha' mnyam gyi sems can thams cad ye
NK016(ma)013:396: nas sangs rgyas yin pa la ma rig 'khrul pa'i
NK016(ma)013:397: dbang gis med snang 'jigs rung 'khor ba'i gnas na
NK016(ma)013:398: sdug bsngal gyi rgyu 'bras la rtag par spyod pa
NK016(ma)013:399: 'di rnams bla na med pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go
NK016(ma)013:401: de'i ched du kun rdzob byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK016(ma)013:402: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)013:403: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK016(ma)013:404: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK016(ma)013:405: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK016(ma)013:407: gnyis pa don dam sems bskyed ni /
NK016(ma)013:408: de ltar rang sems lhag pa bden gnyis zung 'jug
NK016(ma)013:409: dbyer med kyi don la blo 'byor ba'am skye ba'i
NK016(ma)013:410: ched du don dam byang chub kyi mchog tu sems
NK016(ma)013:412: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK016(ma)013:413: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK016(ma)013:414: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK016(ma)013:415: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK016(ma)013:416: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK016(ma)013:417: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK016(ma)013:420: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK016(ma)013:421: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK016(ma)013:422: gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK016(ma)013:423: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK016(ma)013:424: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK016(ma)013:425: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK016(ma)013:426: dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK016(ma)013:427: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK016(ma)013:428: e ma 'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK016(ma)013:429: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK016(ma)013:433: drug pa me tog dor ba ni /
NK016(ma)013:434: sngar gtad pa'i me tog nyid thal mo'i bar du
NK016(ma)013:435: bzung ba nyid slob dpon gyi lus gdod nas rigs
NK016(ma)013:436: lnga'i dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa la 'dor bar gsungs
NK016(ma)013:437: kyang / 'dir 'jug pa bde phyir man+dala gyi ra ba 'di nyid rigs lnga'i lhar bzhugs pa la /
NK016(ma)013:438: de yang ngo bo ye shes gcig las gtso 'khor
NK016(ma)013:439: gyi rnam par shar ba ma gtogs don la bzang
NK016(ma)013:440: ngan med kyang rang gi sngon las kyis 'brel ba'i
NK016(ma)013:441: lha de la 'bab par shog snyam du 'di'i rjes
NK016(ma)013:443: slob dpon sku yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK016(ma)013:444: rin chen me tog 'di dor bas /
NK016(ma)013:445: rnam par dag pa'i las gang gis /
NK016(ma)013:446: thugs rjes mnyes par bgyid mdzad lha //
NK016(ma)013:447: gang yin de la 'bab par shog /
NK016(ma)013:449: pra ti sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)013:450: bo d+hi tsit+tasa ma ya stam /
NK016(ma)013:451: zhes me tog dor tu bcug nas gang la babs pa'i rigs nges par byas te /
NK016(ma)013:452: dbus su babs na rdo rje'i rigs /
NK016(ma)013:453: shar du de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs /
NK016(ma)013:456: byang du las kyi rigs te rigs gang yin ngos bzung nas /
NK016(ma)013:458: dbus su babs na rdo rje snying po rtsal /
NK016(ma)013:465: rdo rje dbyings phyug rtsal lta bu /
NK016(ma)013:470: rdo rje bee ro tsa na rtsal /
NK016(ma)013:476: rdo rje yon tan gter 'byung rtsal /
NK016(ma)013:478: rdo rje rin chen snying po rtsal /
NK016(ma)013:486: rdo rje ma chags pad+ma rtsal /
NK016(ma)013:500: zhes pa lta bu rigs dang mthun pa'i ming gdags /
NK016(ma)013:501: bdun pa me tog gi dbang ni /
NK016(ma)013:502: de nas sngar phul ba'i me tog gi phreng ba
NK016(ma)013:503: de gang la babs pa'i lha des slar yang dbang
NK016(ma)013:504: / rtags cod pan gyi tshul du dbang bskur bar bsam la /
NK016(ma)013:506: dam tshig bden pa chen po'i mthus //
NK016(ma)013:507: sngon sbyangs las kyi 'brel ba dang //
NK016(ma)013:508: gnyis su med pa'i mthu stobs kyis //
NK016(ma)013:509: mnyam par byin rlabs mdzad du gsol //
NK016(ma)013:511: badz+ra sa t+aa a be sha ya +aah zhes me tog gi phreng ba mgo bor bcing /
NK016(ma)013:512: brgyad pa mig dbye ba ni /
NK016(ma)013:513: de nas ma rig pa'i ling tog mig dar dang lhan cig tu bsal ba'i mos pa mdzod /
NK016(ma)013:515: ji ltar mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK016(ma)013:516: ma rig ldongs pa bsal ba ltar //
NK016(ma)013:517: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs kyi lhas //
NK016(ma)013:518: skal ldan bu khyod mig phye'o //
NK016(ma)013:520: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK016(ma)013:521: ces brjod la gser thur thogs te mig dbye ba'i rgyas gdong g.yogs bsal /
NK016(ma)013:522: dgu pa mthong ba bstan pa ni /
NK016(ma)013:525: da ni dad pa rab tu bskyed //
NK016(ma)013:526: khyod ni sangs rgyas rigs su skyes //
NK016(ma)013:527: sngags dang phyag rgyas byin gyis brlabs //
NK016(ma)013:528: dngos grub thams cad phun sum tshogs //
NK016(ma)013:529: dam tshig mchog tu khyod 'gyur ro //
NK016(ma)013:531: de nas ye shes kyi mig gsar du thob pa
NK016(ma)013:532: de la mthong ba bstan pa blta bar bskul ba
NK016(ma)013:533: ni / de yang 'og gzhi 'byung ba rim brtsegs
NK016(ma)013:534: dang bcas pa'i ri rab kyi steng du ye shes
NK016(ma)013:535: rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang phyi nang
NK016(ma)013:536: gnyis rim gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa /
NK016(ma)013:537: nang nas rim pa gzhin mthing dkar ser dmar ljang
NK016(ma)013:538: ba'i rtsig pa rim pa lnga dang ldan pa'i steng
NK016(ma)013:539: du rin po che'i pha gu ser po la rin
NK016(ma)013:540: po che sna tshogs pas bkra ba 'phyar stabs su
NK016(ma)013:541: bkod pa'i mthar mu tig gi mgul 'khor 'chang ba
NK016(ma)013:542: / de'i steng du bre phul gyi snam bu la
NK016(ma)013:543: gser gyi ska rags bzhi'i phyi ngos su ma ka
NK016(ma)013:544: ra'i kha nas rin po che'i d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa
NK016(ma)013:545: / ba phyed pa / dar dang rnga yab dril bu dang me long /
NK016(ma)013:546: zla ba rlung gis bskyod pa la sogs pas mdzes pa /
NK016(ma)013:547: de'i phyi ngos su bya 'dabs las 'phyang ba'i rin po che'i shar bu /
NK016(ma)013:548: steng ngos su mda' yab pad+ma 'dab ma phyed pa'i dbyibs can /
NK016(ma)013:549: de dag gi bar bar du bum pa la gnas pa'i rgyal mtshan dang /
NK016(ma)013:550: zur bzhir rnam par bkra ba'i gdugs kyis brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)013:551: rim pa gnyis ka'i rtsig pa'i 'gram nas 'dod yon
NK016(ma)013:552: gyi snam bu dmar pos bskor ba la gzugs rdo
NK016(ma)013:553: rje la sogs lha mo rnams kyis mchod sprin rab
NK016(ma)013:554: 'byams spro ba / sgo dang sgo khyud kyi mtshams
NK016(ma)013:555: dang zur bzhir zla ba phyed pa la gnas pa'i
NK016(ma)013:556: rdo rje nor bus brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)013:557: phyi ma'i sgo khang them skas dang bcas pa'i sgo
NK016(ma)013:558: logs kyi zur bzhi nas bum pa la gnas pa'i
NK016(ma)013:559: ka ba bzhis btegs pa'i rta babs snam bu brgyad
NK016(ma)013:560: pa bsil khang dang ldan pa'i rtse mor pad+ma la
NK016(ma)013:561: gnas pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo gdugs kyis phub pa
NK016(ma)013:562: g.yas g.yon du ri dwags pho mo dang bcas pa
NK016(ma)013:563: / gzhan yang gdugs dang rgyal mtshan /
NK016(ma)013:564: ba dan sna tshogs pa dang gser gyi dril bu la sogs pas brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)013:565: sgo'i g.yas g.yon gyi gzhi la t+wa la'i ljon pa
NK016(ma)013:566: dang dpag bsam gyi shing la bkra shis pa'i bya
NK016(ma)013:567: snyan par sgrog pa sna tshogs gnas pa /
NK016(ma)013:568: shing de dag kyang gser gyi tha gus bres shing
NK016(ma)013:569: dril bu dang g.yer kha chos kyi sgra snyan par
NK016(ma)013:571: yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'i khrus kyi rdzing bu la lha mo sna tshogs bde bar rtse ba /
NK016(ma)013:572: rin po che'i phung po 'od 'bar ba re re ste brgyad dang /
NK016(ma)013:573: gzhan yang rin po che sna bdun dang /
NK016(ma)013:574: bkra shis pa'i rdzas brgyad sogs 'dod pa'i yon tan thams cad kyis mdzes par gang ba'o //
NK016(ma)013:575: gzhal yas khang gi nang bar khyams gru bzhi pa
NK016(ma)013:576: nyis rim gyi nang ma gru chad dang bcas pa'i
NK016(ma)013:577: lte ba re'u mig dgu pa 'khor lo sum rim
NK016(ma)013:578: mu khyud dang bcas pas bskor ba'i phyogs bzhi nas
NK016(ma)013:579: rigs kyi mtshan ma can gyi ka ba brgyad kyis
NK016(ma)013:580: btegs pa'i rdo rje'i gdung zlum dang /
NK016(ma)013:581: gdung chen bzhis mig mang ris su bris pas mdzes
NK016(ma)013:582: par phub pa'i dbus phyur bur gyur pa'i rtse mor
NK016(ma)013:583: rdo rje rin po che'i tog gis mdzes pa /
NK016(ma)013:584: phyi nang gnyis ka'i steng 'og thams cad shar dkar /
NK016(ma)013:588: dbus sngo ba dwangs shing sgrib pa med pa kun
NK016(ma)013:589: tu gsal ba sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte ba la
NK016(ma)013:590: rdzogs pa / de'i phyi rol du r+au dra longs
NK016(ma)013:591: spyod dang bcas pa dbyings su bsgral ba'i dur khrod
NK016(ma)013:592: rdzogs pa / chen po brgyad / dur khrod kyi
NK016(ma)013:593: chas rnams kyis 'jigs par byas pa'i phyi nas rdo
NK016(ma)013:594: rje srung ba'i gur khang 'bar ba me'i 'od zer
NK016(ma)013:595: kun tu 'phro bas yongs su bskor ba'i lha gnas
NK016(ma)013:596: so sor gdan gyi rim pa ni /
NK016(ma)013:597: gtso bo dang de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga'i gnas su seng ge /
NK016(ma)013:601: shang shang rnams kyis btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri
NK016(ma)013:602: drug gi steng du pad nyi zla ba ste lnga
NK016(ma)013:603: brtsegs / che mchog dang khrag 'thung dgu'i gnas su
NK016(ma)013:604: pad zla nyi ma'i steng dregs pa can khyo shugs
NK016(ma)013:605: brtsegs / zung re / sems dpa' brgyad kyi gnas su pad nyi zla ba /
NK016(ma)013:608: sgo skyong bzhi rnams kyi gnas su nyi ma dang zhing gi gdan re re /
NK016(ma)013:609: thub pa drug gi gnas su pad rkyang dang /
NK016(ma)013:610: dbang mo rnams kyi gnas su zhing skam po'i gdan re re ste /
NK016(ma)013:611: de rnams ni rten dkyil 'khor ro //
NK016(ma)013:613: de lta bu'i gzhal yas khang gi dbus kyi gdan
NK016(ma)013:614: la yid kyi rnam shes gnas su dag pa bcom
NK016(ma)013:615: ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po sku mdog mthing
NK016(ma)013:616: ga in+d+ra n+ai la'i lhun po la nyi ma shar
NK016(ma)013:617: ba ltar 'od zer rab tu 'bar ba zhal gcig
NK016(ma)013:618: phyag gnyis pa / zhi zhing rab tu 'dzum pa'i
NK016(ma)013:619: mdangs gsal ba'i zhal gyi 'gyur pa ting nge 'dzin
NK016(ma)013:620: gyis rnam par rol pa'i nyams can mtshan dang dpe
NK016(ma)013:622: phyag gnyis mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya can /
NK016(ma)013:623: rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'i pang du
NK016(ma)013:624: chos kyi ngo bo gnas su dag pa yum kun
NK016(ma)013:625: tu bzang mo mthing ga zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma
NK016(ma)013:626: / phyag gnyis kyis yab la 'khyud cing pad+ma'i skyil mo krung gis 'khril ba /
NK016(ma)013:627: gnyis ka'ang lha rdzas kyi dar dkar po gser gyi
NK016(ma)013:628: ngang ris can gyi stod g.yogs dang tshi ku'i smad
NK016(ma)013:629: dkris kha dog sna tshogs pa'i cod pan /
NK016(ma)013:632: dar gyi chas gos lnga dang /
NK016(ma)013:639: phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu ste /
NK016(ma)013:640: rin po che'i rgyan brgyad kyis mdzes par spras pa /
NK016(ma)013:641: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can /
NK016(ma)013:642: gsal 'tsher lhun stug gzi byin ldan pa ste /
NK016(ma)013:643: zhi ba'i nyams dgu rgyas pa /
NK016(ma)013:644: sangs rgyas kyi sprin phung mtha' yas par 'char ba'i
NK016(ma)013:645: 'od zer kha dog drug gi snang ba re re
NK016(ma)013:646: yang bye ba phrag drug drug 'phro zhing 'bar ba'i
NK016(ma)013:647: klong na bde stong gnyis su med pa'i ngo bor
NK016(ma)013:648: bzhugs pa'o / gtso ba'i g.yas su rnam shes kyi
NK016(ma)013:649: phung po dag 'byung ba nam mkha'i khams gnas su
NK016(ma)013:650: dag pa thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das
NK016(ma)013:651: rdo rje'i mi bskyod pa dang yum rdo rje dbyings
NK016(ma)013:652: bzhugs pa'o / phyug ma / de'i phyi rol gyi re'u mig la /
NK016(ma)013:653: shar du gzugs phung dang 'byung ba sa'i khams gnas
NK016(ma)013:654: su dag pa sku rdo rje bdag nyid bcom ldan
NK016(ma)013:655: 'das rnam par snang mdzad dang yum sangs rgyas spyan
NK016(ma)013:656: ma / lho ru tshor phung dang 'byung ba chu'i
NK016(ma)013:657: khams gnas su dag pa yon tan rdo rje'i bdag
NK016(ma)013:658: nyid bcom ldan 'das rin chen 'byung gnas dang yum
NK016(ma)013:659: ma / m+aa ma k+ai / nub tu 'du shes
NK016(ma)013:660: kyi phung po dang 'byung ba me'i khams gnas su
NK016(ma)013:661: dag pa gsung rdo rje'i bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das
NK016(ma)013:662: snang ba mtha' yas dang yum gos dkar mo /
NK016(ma)013:663: byang du 'du byed kyi phung po dang 'byung ba
NK016(ma)013:664: rlung gi khams gnas su dag pa phrin las rdo
NK016(ma)013:665: rje'i bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das don yod grub pa
NK016(ma)013:666: dang yum dam tshig sgrol ma ste /
NK016(ma)013:667: yab rnams rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung dang yum rnams brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis rol pa /
NK016(ma)013:668: thams cad kyang rgyan dang cha lugs gtso bo dang mtshungs pa'o //
NK016(ma)013:669: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi gtso bo'i mdun du kun
NK016(ma)013:670: gzhi'i rnam shes gnas su dag pa dpal che mchog
NK016(ma)013:671: he ru ka sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba chen
NK016(ma)013:672: po'i 'od zer can zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK016(ma)013:673: zhal gdangs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK016(ma)013:674: dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum pa /
NK016(ma)013:675: sma ra dang smi na ma dmar ser 'bar zhing dbu skra gyen du 'khyil pa /
NK016(ma)013:677: phyag g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon dmar gyis gang ba'i
NK016(ma)013:678: dung chen steng 'og tu 'dzin pas yum la 'khyud
NK016(ma)013:679: pa / sgeg pa la sogs pa gar dgu'i nyams kyi rol pa /
NK016(ma)013:680: zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang glang po che'i ko
NK016(ma)013:681: bas stod g.yogs shing stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs
NK016(ma)013:682: grol ba / thod pa skam po lnga rigs lnga'i
NK016(ma)013:683: rtse phran can gyi dbu rgyan dang rlon pa lnga
NK016(ma)013:685: rus pa'i rgyan drug dang sbrul gyi chun pos brgyan pa /
NK016(ma)013:686: khrag zhag thal ba sogs dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas can /
NK016(ma)013:688: g.yas brkyang pa'i dor stabs kyis dbang phyug khyo shug
NK016(ma)013:689: gi mgo dang nu ma nas bardzisa pa'i phang du
NK016(ma)013:690: yid chos gnas su dag pa yum gnam zhal dbyings
NK016(ma)013:691: kyi dbang phyug ma sngon mo gcer bu skra grol
NK016(ma)013:693: g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud cing g.yon dung dmar stobs pa'i tshul du 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)013:694: gzig gi pags pa'i sham thabs sogs dur khrod rol pa'i chas can /
NK016(ma)013:695: zhabs g.yon brkyang zhing g.yas bskum pas gtso bo dang dgyes par 'khril ba /
NK016(ma)013:696: stong pa nyid dang snying rje dbyer med pa'i bdag nyid can /
NK016(ma)013:697: ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar pa'i klong na bzhugs pa'o //
NK016(ma)013:698: gtso bo'i g.yon du zhe sdang dang mkha' sems dag
NK016(ma)013:699: pa thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid rdo rje khrag 'thung
NK016(ma)013:700: yab yum / 'khor lo nang ma brtsibs brgyad pa la rim bzhin /
NK016(ma)013:701: shar du gti mug dang sha khams dag pa sku
NK016(ma)013:702: rdo rje'i bdag nyid sangs rgyas khrag 'thung yab yum
NK016(ma)013:703: / lho ru nga rgyal dang khrag khams dag pa
NK016(ma)013:704: yon tan rdo rje'i bdag nyid rin chen khrag 'thung
NK016(ma)013:705: / yab yum / nub tu 'dod chags dang drod
NK016(ma)013:706: khams dag pa gsung rdo rje'i bdag nyid pad+ma khrag
NK016(ma)013:707: / yab yum / 'thung yab yum / byang du
NK016(ma)013:708: phrag dog dang dbugs khams dag pa phrin las rdo
NK016(ma)013:709: rje'i bdag nyid las kyi khrag 'thung yab yum /
NK016(ma)013:710: shar lhor phyin ci log gi lta ba dang drod
NK016(ma)013:711: skyes kyi rtog pa 'joms pa'i bdag nyid rak+sha he
NK016(ma)013:713: lho nub tu myong byed dang mngal skyes kyi rtog
NK016(ma)013:714: pa 'joms pa'i bdag nyid sa nu he ru ka
NK016(ma)013:715: yab yum / nub byang du skye gnas dang bardzusa
NK016(ma)013:716: skyes kyi rtog pa 'joms pa'i bdag nyid gu h+ya
NK016(ma)013:718: byang shar du reg bya dang sgong skyes rtog pa
NK016(ma)013:719: 'joms pa'i bdag nyid yak+sha he ru ka yab yub
NK016(ma)013:720: ste / thams cad kyang gar dgu'i ros sgeg cing dur khrod rol ba'i chas kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK016(ma)013:721: 'khor lo bar ma rtsibs brgyad pa la rim bzhin /
NK016(ma)013:722: shar du mig shes dang yul gzugs gnas su dag pa sa snying yab yum /
NK016(ma)013:723: lho ru rna ba'i rnam shes dang yul sgra gnas su dag pa nam snying yab yum /
NK016(ma)013:724: nub tu sna'i rnam shes dang yul dri gnas su dag pa spyan ras gzigs yab yum /
NK016(ma)013:725: byang du lce'i rnam shes dang yul ro gnas su dag pa phyag rdor yab yum /
NK016(ma)013:726: shar lhor mig dbang dang 'das pa'i dus gnas su dag pa byams pa yab yum /
NK016(ma)013:727: lho nub tu rna ba'i dbang po dang da ltar
NK016(ma)013:728: gyi dus gnas su dag pa sgrib sel yab yum
NK016(ma)013:729: / nub byang du sna'i dbang po dang ma 'ongs
NK016(ma)013:730: pa'i dus gnas su dag pa kun bzang yab yum
NK016(ma)013:731: / / byang shar du lce'i dbang po dang ma
NK016(ma)013:732: nges pa'i dus gnas su dag pa 'jam dpal yab
NK016(ma)013:733: / / yum ste / yab rnams g.yas brkyang ba'i
NK016(ma)013:734: phyed skyil la yum rnams g.yon brkyang phyed skyil gyis
NK016(ma)013:736: kyang dar gyi na bza' dang rin po che'i rgyan
NK016(ma)013:738: pa'o // 'khor lo phyi ma rtsibs bcu drug pa'i
NK016(ma)013:739: phyogs mtshams brgyad por rnam shes tshogs brgyad gnas su
NK016(ma)013:740: dag pa'i rtags su shar du koo r+ai ma /
NK016(ma)013:747: byang shar du tsan+da l+ai ste gnas kyi ma mo brgyad /
NK016(ma)013:748: de thams cad kyang gcer bu lang tshos sgeg cing khro 'dzum bzhad pa /
NK016(ma)013:749: dur khrod rol pa'i chas can g.yon brkyang ba'i stabs kyis gnas pa'o //

NK016(ma)013:754: spyang gdong ma ste mche ba can bzhi dang /
NK016(ma)013:755: mtshams kyi rtsibs bzhi'i g.yon logs kyi rtsibs rnams su rim pa gzhin rgod gdong ma /

NK016(ma)013:760: zhal can dur khrod 'bar ba'i chas dang ldan pa'o

NK016(ma)013:764: lho ru 'dod chags gnas du dag pa mi'i thub pa /
NK016(ma)013:765: nub byang du gti mug gnas su dag pa byol song gi thub pa /
NK016(ma)013:766: lho nub tu ser sna gnas su dag pa yi dwags kyi thub pa /
NK016(ma)013:767: byang shar du zhe ldang gnas su dag pa dmyal ba'i thub pa ste /
NK016(ma)013:768: thams cad kyang mchog gi sprul sku'i cha byad can 'gro ba'i don la bzhengs ltabs kyis gnas pa'o //
NK016(ma)013:769: khyams nang ma'i sgo phub bzhi la /

NK016(ma)013:771: lho sgor reg bya dang chad par lta ba gnas su dag pa stobs po che yab yum /

NK016(ma)013:774: su dag pa bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yab yum ste
NK016(ma)013:775: / thams cad kyang khro gtum mi bzad pa'i nyams can gyad kyi 'dor stabs su bzhugs pa'o //

NK016(ma)013:781: byang sgor spyang gdong ma dang /

NK016(ma)013:784: pa'i rtags su shar stod nas rim pa bzhin srin
NK016(ma)013:785: mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang /

NK016(ma)013:810: lho sgor rdo rje mo dang /
NK016(ma)013:811: nub sgor bum sna mo dang /
NK016(ma)013:813: thams cad kyang drag mo'i gzugs can dur khrod 'bar
NK016(ma)013:814: ba'i chas kyis brgyan te zhing gi gdan la rol
NK016(ma)013:815: pa'o // gzhan yang dkyil 'khor chen po'i phyir 'khor yug la khro bo chen po yab yum bcu /
NK016(ma)013:819: sprul pa'i ging chen pho mo /
NK016(ma)013:822: 'bar ma brgyad la sogs te sprul pa dang yang
NK016(ma)013:823: sprul bka' sdod dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs mtha' yas
NK016(ma)013:824: pa dang bcas pa rnams kyang rang rang gi rgyan
NK016(ma)013:825: dang cha lugs dang ldan zhing so so'i 'khor gyis
NK016(ma)013:826: bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo nyi ma dang
NK016(ma)013:827: 'od zer gyi tshul du mngon par snang ba'i sgyu
NK016(ma)013:828: 'phrul gyi rol mo bsam gyis mi khyab pas yongs
NK016(ma)013:830: de ltar na zhi khro dam pa rigs brgya'i dkyil
NK016(ma)013:831: 'khor chen po'i rten dang brten par bcas pa thams

NK016(ma)013:833: dga' ba dang spro ba yang dag par bskyed mdzod

NK016(ma)013:837: par song la / de ltar zhugs pa'i phan yon kyang /
NK016(ma)013:839: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //

NK016(ma)013:841: bsod nams brtags pa gang yin pa //

NK016(ma)013:1054: dud 'gro'i gnas su ltung ba las //
NK016(ma)013:1055: skyob phyir dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK016(ma)013:1056: zhes dbang stegs su drangs par bsam /
NK016(ma)013:1059: ma tha ma tha sarba tir+ya ka ga te he tum h+aum phata /
NK016(ma)013:1060: ces bzla zhing yungs thun gyis brab /
NK016(ma)013:1061: de ltar thun rnams me mtshon du gyur te nyon
NK016(ma)013:1062: mongs pa gti mug gi sgo nas bsags pa'i sdig
NK016(ma)013:1063: sgrib thams cad nyi mas ba mo bzhu ba bzhin
NK016(ma)013:1066: de nas slob dpon gyi khrus bum gyis dbang bskur
NK016(ma)013:1067: bas bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun gyis slob ma'i nyon mongs
NK016(ma)013:1068: pa gti mug gi sgo nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib
NK016(ma)013:1069: thams cad dbang po'i sgo dang ba spu'i bu ga
NK016(ma)013:1070: thams cad nas phyir sangs kyis sbyangs te lus shel
NK016(ma)013:1071: gong phyis pa ltar gyur pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK016(ma)013:1073: til gyi gang bu bzhin gang ba'i //
NK016(ma)013:1074: rgyal ba'i bum pa bzung nas ni //
NK016(ma)013:1075: de nyid du ni blugs mdzad pas //
NK016(ma)013:1076: bag chags ma lus dag gyur cig /
NK016(ma)013:1079: ma tha ma tha sogs btags pa brjod bzhin du bkrus nas /
NK016(ma)013:1080: rigs kyi bu 'dis nyon mongs pa gti mug gi
NK016(ma)013:1081: sgo nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib thams cad sh+ain+tam ku
NK016(ma)013:1083: skabs 'dir rnam snang dang mi 'khrugs pa'i gzungs sngags
NK016(ma)013:1084: bzla ba'ang bla ma rnams kyi phyag len gyi rgyun
NK016(ma)013:1085: la snang bas de bzhin du sgrub pa ni /
NK016(ma)013:1086: na mo b+ha ga wa te sarba durga te pa
NK016(ma)013:1087: ri sho d+ha ni r+aa dza ya ta th+aa ga
NK016(ma)013:1088: ta ya ar+ha te sa myak+sam bud+d+ha ya /
NK016(ma)013:1090: sho d+ha ni sho d+ha ni sarba p+aa pam bi
NK016(ma)013:1091: sho d+ha ni shud+d+he bi shud+d+he sarba karma +aa wa
NK016(ma)013:1092: ra ni bi shud+d+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)013:1094: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK016(ma)013:1095: kam ka ni kam ka ni /
NK016(ma)013:1096: ro tsa ni ro tsa ni /
NK016(ma)013:1097: tro ta ni tro ta ni /
NK016(ma)013:1098: t+r+aa sa ni t+r+aa sa ni /
NK016(ma)013:1099: pra ti ha na pra ti ha na /
NK016(ma)013:1100: sarba karma pa ram p+aa ra ni me sarba sa t+wa nany+tsa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)013:1102: rigs kyi bus tshe rabs 'khor ba thog ma med
NK016(ma)013:1103: pa nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib nyon mongs bag chags
NK016(ma)013:1104: skal ba ngan pa dang bkra mi shis pa'i dngos
NK016(ma)013:1105: po thams cad nye bar zhi ste shin tu bkra
NK016(ma)013:1108: de dag ni ngan song gnas 'dren gyi dbang zhes bya ste /
NK016(ma)013:1109: bcud khyad par can sgrub pa la sngon du snod dag par byed pa bzhin no //
NK016(ma)013:1110: gnyis pa yon tan yar 'phel gyi dbang bskur ba la bzhi las /
NK016(ma)013:1111: dang po rdo rje sems dpa' bum pa'i dbang gis lus kyi dri ma sbyang ba ni /
NK016(ma)013:1112: slob bu seng ges btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri
NK016(ma)013:1113: sna tshogs pad+ma dang nyi zla brtsegs pa'i steng du
NK016(ma)013:1114: rdo rje sems dpa' yum dang bcas pa'i rnam pas
NK016(ma)013:1116: de nas bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo
NK016(ma)013:1117: dbyer ma mchis pa la mi phyed dad pa'i gdung
NK016(ma)013:1118: shugs chen pos gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rjes zlos
NK016(ma)013:1119: mdzod // ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK016(ma)013:1120: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK016(ma)013:1121: 'di nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK016(ma)013:1122: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK016(ma)013:1123: ces de ltar gsol ba btab par gyur pa la /
NK016(ma)013:1124: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo tha mi
NK016(ma)013:1125: dad pa'i thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros pas gdan
NK016(ma)013:1126: gsum tshang ba'i dbang gi lha tshogs nam mkha' gang
NK016(ma)013:1127: bar spyan drangs / de rnams kyis bkra shis pa'i
NK016(ma)013:1128: rnam pa du ma dang ldan pas mi bskyod pa'i
NK016(ma)013:1129: ngo bor stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin bum pa'i
NK016(ma)013:1130: chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur bar mos la /
NK016(ma)013:1131: rnam rgyal bum pa thogs te /
NK016(ma)013:1132: sku gsum dang tshig las byung ba //
NK016(ma)013:1133: nyon mongs zhe sdang 'joms pa yi //
NK016(ma)013:1134: lha yi bdud rtsi dag pa 'dis //
NK016(ma)013:1135: mi bskyod pa ru dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1136: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK016(ma)013:1137: zhes bum chu spyi bor gtigs la dbang bskur zhing bum chu blud do //
NK016(ma)013:1138: de ltar mi bskyod pa'i rang bzhin stong pa nyid
NK016(ma)013:1139: kyi ye shes kyi chu rgyun gyi dbang bskur bas
NK016(ma)013:1141: bde ba chen po'i ye shes nyams su myong /
NK016(ma)013:1142: dbang gnas su bdud rtsi'i dwangs ma 'khyil ba las
NK016(ma)013:1143: mi bskyod pa sprul sku'i cha byad can gyis dbu
NK016(ma)013:1145: de ltar na skal sdan rig pa 'a dzin pa khyod kyi zhe sdang dag /
NK016(ma)013:1146: rnam par shes pa'i phung po mi bskyod par gnas gyur /
NK016(ma)013:1147: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes mngon du byas pa yin no //
NK016(ma)013:1150: nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis
NK016(ma)013:1151: rin 'byung gi ngo bor mnyam pa nyid kyi chu
NK016(ma)013:1152: rgyun gyis dbang bskur bar mos la /
NK016(ma)013:1153: sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyal srid che //
NK016(ma)013:1154: ser sna'i rtog pa rnam par 'joms //
NK016(ma)013:1155: rtag tu chags med sbyin pa 'dis //
NK016(ma)013:1156: rdzogs sangs rgyas su dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1157: ma h+aa sa na t+aa dz+ny+aa na a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK016(ma)013:1158: zhes dbu rgyan mgo bor bkon zhing /
NK016(ma)013:1159: rna ltag g.yas su bum chu gtigs /
NK016(ma)013:1160: de ltar rin 'byung gi rang bzhin mnyam pa nyid
NK016(ma)013:1161: kyi ye shes kyi chu rgyun gyi dbang bskur bas
NK016(ma)013:1163: bde ba chen po'i ye shes nyams su myong /
NK016(ma)013:1164: dbang gnas su bdud rtsi'i dwangs ma 'khyil ba las
NK016(ma)013:1165: rin 'byung sprul sku'i cha byad can gyis dbu brgyan
NK016(ma)013:1166: par bsam la / de ltar na skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod kyi ser sna dag /
NK016(ma)013:1167: tshor ba'i phung po rin chen 'byung ldan du gnas gyur /
NK016(ma)013:1168: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes mngon du byas pa yin no //
NK016(ma)013:1170: de nas nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa
NK016(ma)013:1171: rnams kyis snang mtha'i ngo bor so sor rtog pa'i
NK016(ma)013:1172: ye shes kyi chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur bar mos
NK016(ma)013:1173: la / sangs rgyas kun gyi rdo rje'i dbang //
NK016(ma)013:1174: mi phyed rdo rje'i gsang ba las //
NK016(ma)013:1176: rdo rje chos su dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1177: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK016(ma)013:1178: zhes rdo rje lag g.yas su gtad cing ltag par bum chu gtigs /
NK016(ma)013:1179: de ltar snang ba mtha' yas kyi rang bzhin so
NK016(ma)013:1180: sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi chu rgyun gyis dbang
NK016(ma)013:1181: bskur bas lus kyi nang thams cad gang /
NK016(ma)013:1182: bde ba chen po'i ye shes nyams su myong /
NK016(ma)013:1183: dbang gnas su bdud rtsi'i dwangs ma 'khyil ba las
NK016(ma)013:1184: snang ba mtha' yas sprul sku'i cha byad can gyis
NK016(ma)013:1186: de ltar na skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod kyi 'dod chags dag /
NK016(ma)013:1187: 'du shes kyi phung po snang ba mtha' yas su gnas gyur /
NK016(ma)013:1188: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes mngon du byas pa yin no //
NK016(ma)013:1191: nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis
NK016(ma)013:1192: don grub kyi ngo bor bya ba grub pa'i ye
NK016(ma)013:1193: shes kyi chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur bar mos la
NK016(ma)013:1194: / thabs dang shes rab ldan pa yi //
NK016(ma)013:1195: 'gro don mnyam pa med pa yis //
NK016(ma)013:1196: phrag dog rtog pa rnam par 'joms //
NK016(ma)013:1197: gnyis su med par dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1198: ma h+aa kri t+y+aa nush+th+aa na dz+ny+aa na a b+hi shiny+tsha mi /
NK016(ma)013:1199: zhes lag g.yon du dril bu gtad cing rna ltag g.yon du bum chu gtigs /
NK016(ma)013:1200: de ltar don yod grub pa'i rang bzhin bya ba
NK016(ma)013:1201: grub pa'i ye shes kyi chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur
NK016(ma)013:1203: bde ba chen po'i ye shes nyams su myong /
NK016(ma)013:1204: dbang gnas su bdud rtsi'i dwangs ma 'khyil ba las
NK016(ma)013:1205: don grub sprul sku'i cha byad can gyis dbu brgyan
NK016(ma)013:1206: par bsam la / de ltar na skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod kyi phrag dog dag /
NK016(ma)013:1207: 'du byed kyi phung po don yod grub par gnas gyur /
NK016(ma)013:1208: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes mngon du byas pa yin no //
NK016(ma)013:1210: nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis
NK016(ma)013:1211: rnam snang gi ngo bor me long lta bu'i ye
NK016(ma)013:1212: shes kyi chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur bar mos la
NK016(ma)013:1213: / rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur bas //
NK016(ma)013:1214: gti mug rtog pa rnam par 'joms //
NK016(ma)013:1215: cis kyang mi chod mi shigs pa'i //
NK016(ma)013:1216: rdo rje'i ming du rab tu grags //
NK016(ma)013:1217: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na a b+hi shi ny+tsa mi /
NK016(ma)013:1218: zhes rdor dril lag g.yas g.yon du gtad cing bum chu dpral bar gtigs /
NK016(ma)013:1219: de ltar rnam par snang mdzad kyi rang bzhin me
NK016(ma)013:1220: long lta bu'i ye shes kyi chu rgyun gyis dbang
NK016(ma)013:1221: bskur bas lus thams cad gang /
NK016(ma)013:1222: bde ba chen po'i ye shes nyams su myong /
NK016(ma)013:1223: dbang gnas su bdud rtsi'i dwangs ma 'khyil ba las
NK016(ma)013:1224: rnam par snang mdzad sprul sku'i cha byad can gyis
NK016(ma)013:1226: de ltar na skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod kyi gti mug dag /
NK016(ma)013:1227: gzugs kyi phung po rnam par snang mdzad du gan sa gyur /
NK016(ma)013:1228: me long lta bu'i ye shes mngon du byas pa yin no //
NK016(ma)013:1230: de'i mthar sgo gsum rdo rje gsum du byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK016(ma)013:1231: sku'am phyag mtshan nam phyag rgya gnas gsum du bzhag la /
NK016(ma)013:1232: slob bu rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum du gsal
NK016(ma)013:1233: ba'i spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i dkar po
NK016(ma)013:1234: / de yi 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)013:1235: sku rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK016(ma)013:1237: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK016(ma)013:1238: yongs su gyur pa las rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo 'dzin pas rgyas btab pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK016(ma)013:1239: dpal ldan sangs rgyas sku 'chang ba //
NK016(ma)013:1240: rdo rje mi phyed gsum gyi sku //
NK016(ma)013:1241: deng bdag sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK016(ma)013:1242: sku yi dbyig tu dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1243: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ka ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)013:1246: mgrin par pad+ma la gnas pa'i +aam dmar po /
NK016(ma)013:1247: de'i 'od zer gyis de gzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK016(ma)013:1248: gsung rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK016(ma)013:1250: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK016(ma)013:1251: +aam yongs su gyur pa las mtha' dmar po pad+ma 'dzin pas rgyas btab pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK016(ma)013:1252: dpal ldan sangs rgyas gsung 'chang ba //
NK016(ma)013:1253: rdo rje mi phyed gsum gyi gsung //
NK016(ma)013:1254: deng bdag sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK016(ma)013:1255: gsung gi dbyig tu dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1256: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra swa wa +aa t+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)013:1258: snying khar nyi ma la gnas pa'i h+aum sngon po /
NK016(ma)013:1259: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskur /
NK016(ma)013:1260: thugs rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK016(ma)013:1262: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK016(ma)013:1263: h'u yongs su gyur pa las mi bskyod pa sngon
NK016(ma)013:1264: po rdo rje 'dzin pas rgyas btab pa'i mos pa
NK016(ma)013:1265: mdzod / dpal ldan sangs rgyas thugs 'chang ba //
NK016(ma)013:1266: rdo rje mi phyed gsum gyi thugs //
NK016(ma)013:1267: deng bdag sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK016(ma)013:1268: thugs kyi dbyig tu dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1269: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)013:1270: zhes dbang bskur zhing sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum du nga rgyal bya'o //
NK016(ma)013:1271: de ltar dbang bskur bas lus ngag yid gsum lha'i
NK016(ma)013:1272: sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum du gyur pa nyid
NK016(ma)013:1273: mchod pa'i yul du bzang ba yin pas mnga' gsol
NK016(ma)013:1278: gnyis pa mkha' 'gro ma gtor ma'i dbang gis gsang ba'i ye shes byin dbab pa ni /
NK016(ma)013:1279: slob bu lus kyi gnad gcer bur phyungs /
NK016(ma)013:1280: rkang pa rting sprad nas rtse mo btsugs /
NK016(ma)013:1282: lag gnyis gru mo phyir brgyangs pas spyi bor gtor ma bzung /
NK016(ma)013:1283: rtsa dang nywa bzhi grim gyis sgrim pa ni lus kyi las so //
NK016(ma)013:1285: sarba r+au pa ba lim ta p+au dza kha kha kh+aa ti kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)013:1287: gang shar rtsol med du klod la smrar gzhug /
NK016(ma)013:1288: sems kyi las snod kyi 'jig rten b+hany+dza 'bar ba'i
NK016(ma)013:1289: gtor gzhong du rgya tshad med pa'i zla ba la
NK016(ma)013:1290: gnas pa'i bcud kyi sems can thams cad kyi lus
NK016(ma)013:1291: dang longs spyod dge ba'i rtsa ba dang bcas pa
NK016(ma)013:1292: thams cad / phung khams kyi chos can rang bzhin
NK016(ma)013:1293: lhun grub dam tshig gi rdzas su dag pa la
NK016(ma)013:1294: thams cad / / spyi bo'i gtor ma ye shes
NK016(ma)013:1295: lnga'i rang bzhin bdud rtsi'i dwangs ma sangs rgyas thams
NK016(ma)013:1296: cad kyi ye shes dang ro mnyam pa chu bo'i
NK016(ma)013:1297: rgyun bzhin du babs nas ro gcig tu 'dren pa'i
NK016(ma)013:1298: bdud rtsi'i mchod sprin mkha' khyab tu spel bas 'khor
NK016(ma)013:1299: 'das thams cad mchod yul du dag pa'i sku gsung
NK016(ma)013:1300: thugs kyi gsang ba rang bzhin dbyings kyi mkha' 'gro
NK016(ma)013:1301: mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo dang /
NK016(ma)013:1302: slob ma'i lung ngag yid gsum ro gcig pa bde
NK016(ma)013:1303: ba chen po'i ye shes 'bar ba la sems rtse
NK016(ma)013:1304: gcig tu ma yengs pa mdzod /
NK016(ma)013:1305: ces brjod la cang te'u sogs rol mo'i sgra dal brel spel ma dang /
NK016(ma)013:1306: sha chen gyi spos sreg pa dang bcas pas 'khor
NK016(ma)013:1307: 'das thams cad dag pa rab 'byams rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK016(ma)013:1308: 'khor chen por yongs su sad par byas la /
NK016(ma)013:1310: kun bzang phyag rdor ku ku r+aa dza che //
NK016(ma)013:1311: in+d+ra b+hu ti shakya pu tra'i zhabs //
NK016(ma)013:1312: sid+ha r+aa dza u pa r+aa dza la //
NK016(ma)013:1313: gsol ba 'debs so byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK016(ma)013:1314: go ma de bi rdo rje h+aum mdzad rtsal //
NK016(ma)013:1315: sangs rgyas gsang ba bi ma la mi tra //
NK016(ma)013:1316: gnyags lo gzhon nu sog po lha dpal la //
NK016(ma)013:1317: gsol ba gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes sru legs sgron //
NK016(ma)013:1318: sras mchog gzhon snying zhu ston bsod nams mtshan //
NK016(ma)013:1319: bde gshegs zur chen zur chung shes rab grags //
NK016(ma)013:1320: gsol ba glan dang 'gar ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan dpal //
NK016(ma)013:1321: rdor 'od bsod nams rgyal mtshan chos seng zhabs //
NK016(ma)013:1322: sangs rgyas dpal ba bsod nams mgon po la //
NK016(ma)013:1323: gsol ba sgrol chen bsam rdor thugs sras sangs rin zhabs //
NK016(ma)013:1324: 'gos lo gzhon dpal bsod nams rgya mtsho'i sde //
NK016(ma)013:1325: se ston rin rgyan rgya hor rdo rje rtsal //
NK016(ma)013:1326: gsol pan chen pad+ma dbang rgyal bdud 'joms rje //
NK016(ma)013:1327: tshe ring dbang po ngag dbang phun tshogs mtshan //
NK016(ma)013:1328: brgyud srol kun 'dus rig 'dzin gter bdag gling //
NK016(ma)013:1329: gsol ba lo chen chos dpal rgyas sras rin rnam zhabs //
NK016(ma)013:1330: pad+ma bstan 'dzin phrin las rnam par rgyal //
NK016(ma)013:1331: phrin las chos sgron sangs rgyas kun dag'i dpal //
NK016(ma)013:1332: gsol ba bstan 'dzin nor bu phan bde'i 'od zer 'bar //
NK016(ma)013:1333: khyab dag drin chen rtsa brgyud bla ma dang //
NK016(ma)013:1334: rab 'byams zhi khro dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i lhar //
NK016(ma)013:1335: gsol ba 'debs so byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK016(ma)013:1336: +aahh+aum bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na
NK016(ma)013:1337: d+h+aa tu ah ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum
NK016(ma)013:1338: phata / ces bla ma brgyud pa'i mtshan shar dang /
NK016(ma)013:1339: yi dam zhi khro'i sngags brjod pa'i mthar /
NK016(ma)013:1341: rtsa brgyud kyi bla ma dam pa rnams dang yi
NK016(ma)013:1342: dam zhi khro rab 'byams sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK016(ma)013:1344: dam can chos skyong rigs drug gi sems can lha'i
NK016(ma)013:1345: 'khor lor dag pa dang bcas pa thams cad la
NK016(ma)013:1346: slob bu'i lus longs spyod dge tshogs rgya mtsho dang
NK016(ma)013:1347: bcas pa thams cad srid zhi dbyer med kyi bdud
NK016(ma)013:1348: rtsi chen por sbyar zhing spel ba 'di 'bul zhing
NK016(ma)013:1349: mchis na gnyis su med par bzhes te gnas skabs
NK016(ma)013:1350: dang mthar thug gi phyi nang gsang ba'i bar chad
NK016(ma)013:1351: mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad zhi ba dang /
NK016(ma)013:1352: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa stsal du gsol //
NK016(ma)013:1357: rigs drug gi sems can lha'i 'khor lor dag pa
NK016(ma)013:1358: rnams la zhes tha dad du phye na'ang legs par
NK016(ma)013:1359: 'gyur ro // de ltar byin phabs pas lus 'phar zhing g.yo ba dang /
NK016(ma)013:1360: ngag smra zhing rgod pa dang sems rtog med 'od
NK016(ma)013:1361: gsal gyi dbyings su grol ba'i nyams rnams byung rgyal
NK016(ma)013:1363: de nas gtor ma gnas su bzhag nas bla ma
NK016(ma)013:1364: la spyi bos gtugs pa'i phyag bya zhing yon dbul
NK016(ma)013:1365: lo // gsum pa kun tu bzang po rig pa
NK016(ma)013:1366: rtsal gyi dbang gis lhag pa'i ye shes ngo sprod
NK016(ma)013:1368: dang po rtags kun tu bzang po mtshon par byed pa ni /
NK016(ma)013:1370: thal mo sbyar ba dang bcas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK016(ma)013:1372: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun bdag nyid //
NK016(ma)013:1373: rdo rje bla ma dgongs su gsol //
NK016(ma)013:1374: yang dag don gyi mchog dam pa //
NK016(ma)013:1375: bdag la mngon du 'gyur bar mdzod //
NK016(ma)013:1377: de nas slob bu stan bde ba la lus rnam snang gi chos bdun bcas la /
NK016(ma)013:1378: sems kyi rten snying gar kun tu bzang po mthing
NK016(ma)013:1379: ga mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya can rdo rje'i skyil
NK016(ma)013:1380: mo krung gis pad zla la bzhugs par bskyed la
NK016(ma)013:1382: zhes pas ye shes pa spyan drangs /
NK016(ma)013:1383: dzahh+aum bam hohs gnyis med du bstim la /
NK016(ma)013:1384: rdo rje rtse lnga pa gtad de /
NK016(ma)013:1385: 'dir ni rang rig 'gyur ba med pa'i don ye shes lngar mtshon pa'i rtags yin no //
NK016(ma)013:1387: gnyis pa don kun tu bzang po ngo sprad pa ni /
NK016(ma)013:1389: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin 'di //
NK016(ma)013:1390: kun tu bzang pos ston par dka' //
NK016(ma)013:1391: ming tsam 'di zhes brjod pa ni //
NK016(ma)013:1392: rdo rje sems dpas mtshon du med //
NK016(ma)013:1393: rig pa sems kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK016(ma)013:1394: spros med rnam dag ye shes yin //
NK016(ma)013:1395: kun gzhi ye nas ma bcos pa //
NK016(ma)013:1396: bde chen rang shar klong du zhog /
NK016(ma)013:1397: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK016(ma)013:1400: phyi ma ma skyes pa'i da ltar gyi shes pa
NK016(ma)013:1401: skad cig ma gang skyes de ka bsal bzhag med
NK016(ma)013:1403: de ltar bzhag pas sems kyi gshis gang du'ang ma grub pa /
NK016(ma)013:1404: mdangs bde chen du ma 'gags pa /
NK016(ma)013:1405: rtsal sna tshogs su snang ba bsgom bya sgom byed
NK016(ma)013:1406: thams cad las 'das pa'i gsal rig rjen ne ba
NK016(ma)013:1407: spros pa dang bral ba de ka ye shes lnga'i
NK016(ma)013:1408: rang bzhin don kun tu bzang po yin no //
NK016(ma)013:1410: gsum pa nyams kun tu bzang po bskyang du gzhug pa ni /
NK016(ma)013:1412: snang stong dbyer med chos sku la //
NK016(ma)013:1413: rig stong bde ba chen por shar //
NK016(ma)013:1415: kun tu bzang po'i ngo bo'o //
NK016(ma)013:1416: bod+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa tu
NK016(ma)013:1417: +aah zhes pas rjes shes gang shar gyi skye 'gag
NK016(ma)013:1418: gnas gsum gyi rang ngo la bltas pas rang grol
NK016(ma)013:1419: gyi ye shes gsal la mi rtog pa ni nyams
NK016(ma)013:1420: kun tu bzang po yin te /
NK016(ma)013:1422: sngar rjes mi bcad 'das pa'i 'du shes dor //
NK016(ma)013:1423: phyis sngun mi bsu yid kyi 'brel thag bcad //
NK016(ma)013:1424: bar du 'dzin med nam mkha'i ngang du bzhag /
NK016(ma)013:1426: de ltar gsum gyi dang pos mtshon bya don gyi
NK016(ma)013:1427: ye shes nyid mtshon byed dape'am rtags la brten nas
NK016(ma)013:1429: gnyis pas rang gnas kyi ye shes de nyid da
NK016(ma)013:1430: ltar gyi sems skad cig ma bzhi cha gsum bral
NK016(ma)013:1431: gyi steng du rig pa gcer bu zang thal rjen
NK016(ma)013:1433: gsum pas don de nyid rjes shes kyi snang bas
NK016(ma)013:1434: bsal bzhag skye 'gag 'gro 'ong med par chu bo'i
NK016(ma)013:1435: rgyun bzhin bskyangs pas 'bras bu gzhi thog tu rang
NK016(ma)013:1437: bzhi pa dam pa rigs brgya'i phyag rgya'i dbang gis
NK016(ma)013:1438: dag pa'i snang ba rab 'byams su bstan pa ni
NK016(ma)013:1439: / slob bu seng ges btegs pa'i khri la bcom
NK016(ma)013:1440: lngan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po yum dang bcas
NK016(ma)013:1441: pa'i rnam pas 'khod pa la dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK016(ma)013:1442: tshogs rnams mar me gcig las gnyis chad kyi tshul
NK016(ma)013:1443: du rim bzhin byon nas so so'i gnas su gnyis
NK016(ma)013:1444: med du thim pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK016(ma)013:1445: ces brjod la sku rnams rim gyis thogs la dbang bskur ba ni /
NK016(ma)013:1447: kun gzhi gsang ba dag pa'i dbyings nas yid rang
NK016(ma)013:1448: byung gi ye shes rang shes rig gi rgyal po
NK016(ma)013:1449: / yid byed pa po dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi yab /
NK016(ma)013:1450: chags med skyon dang bral bas gdan pad+ma la bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)013:1451: sangs rgyas dang sems can mnyam par mkhyen pas phyag mnyam pa'i phyag rgya can /
NK016(ma)013:1452: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi mnga' bdag bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1453: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad don dam par
NK016(ma)013:1454: chos kyi dbyings su sdud ma chos can mtshan ma'i
NK016(ma)013:1455: skyon gyis ma gos pas gdan pad+ma la bzhugs pa
NK016(ma)013:1456: / kun la khyab par gnas pas phyag mnyam pa'i phyag rgya can /
NK016(ma)013:1457: chos bya ba mo dkyil 'khor thams cad bskyed pa'i gzhi /
NK016(ma)013:1458: yum kun tu bzang mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1460: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta ah a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK016(ma)013:1461: don dam par sems can gyi rnam par shes pa'i
NK016(ma)013:1462: phung po gnas su dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa
NK016(ma)013:1463: thams cad kyi thugs kyi bdag nyid /
NK016(ma)013:1464: mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri can /
NK016(ma)013:1465: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis skye shi dang 'pho 'gyur gyi rtog pa mi mnga' bas /
NK016(ma)013:1467: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje mi skyod pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1468: don dam par 'byung ba nam mkha'i ngo bo gnas
NK016(ma)013:1469: su dag pa yum chen mo kun tu bzang mo
NK016(ma)013:1470: // dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad 'byung ba'i gnas /
NK016(ma)013:1471: yum chen mo nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1473: mum d+h+aa t+we shwa r+ai a b+hi shi ny+tsa mi /
NK016(ma)013:1474: don dam par sems can gyi gzugs kyi phung po
NK016(ma)013:1475: gnas su dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK016(ma)013:1476: kyi sku'i bdag nyid stobs glang po che'i khri can
NK016(ma)013:1477: / me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis kun la dbang bsgyur bas phyag rgya 'khor lo can /
NK016(ma)013:1478: bcom ldan 'das dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1479: don dam par 'byung ba sa'i ngo bo gnas su dag pa yum chen mo sangs rgyas spyan ma /
NK016(ma)013:1480: dus gsum kyi rgyal ba thams cad bskyed pa'i gzhi /
NK016(ma)013:1481: yum chen mo bud+d+ha dbyings phyug ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1483: l+aam dwe sha ra ti a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK016(ma)013:1484: don dam par sems can gyi tshor ba'i phung po
NK016(ma)013:1485: gnas su dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK016(ma)013:1486: kyi yon tan gyi bdag nyid shugs 'chang rta'i khri
NK016(ma)013:1487: can / mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes las ma
NK016(ma)013:1488: g.yos par che ba'i yon tan thams cad 'byung bas
NK016(ma)013:1489: phyag rgya rin po che 'bar ba can /
NK016(ma)013:1490: bcom ldan 'das dpal rin chen 'byung ldan gyi dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1491: don dam par 'byung ba chu'i ngo bo gnas su dag pa yum chen mo m+aa ma k+ai /
NK016(ma)013:1492: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad kyi yon tan gyi gter 'dzin ma /
NK016(ma)013:1493: yum chen mo rin chen dbyings phyug ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1497: don dam par sems can gyi 'du shes kyi phung
NK016(ma)013:1498: po gnas su dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK016(ma)013:1499: cad kyi gsung gi bdag nyid mdzes byed rma bya'i
NK016(ma)013:1500: khri can / so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyis
NK016(ma)013:1501: chos thams cad kyi spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid
NK016(ma)013:1502: gsal la ma chags par gzigs pas phyag rgya pad+ma
NK016(ma)013:1503: khri can / can / bcom ldan 'das dpal snang ba mtha' yas kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1504: don dam par 'byung ba me'i ngo bo gnas su dag pa yum chen mo na bza' dkar mo /
NK016(ma)013:1505: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi gsung mchog ma /
NK016(ma)013:1506: yum chen mo pad+ma dbyings phyug ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1508: p+aam r+aa ga ra ti a b+hi shany+tsa mi /
NK016(ma)013:1509: don dam par sems can gyi 'du byed kyi phung
NK016(ma)013:1510: po gnas su dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK016(ma)013:1511: cad kyi phrin las kyi bdag nyid cang shes shang
NK016(ma)013:1513: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi phrin las mthar
NK016(ma)013:1514: phyin par mdzad pas phyag rgya rdo rje rgya gram
NK016(ma)013:1515: can / bcom ldan 'das dpal don yod grub pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1516: don dam par 'byung ba rlung gi ngo bo gnas
NK016(ma)013:1517: su dag pa yum chen mo dam tshig sgrol ma
NK016(ma)013:1518: / 'gro ba rnams 'phags pa'i sa bcur sgrol ma /
NK016(ma)013:1519: yum chen mo las kyi dbyings phyug ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1521: t+aam badz+ra ra ti a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NK016(ma)013:1522: don dam par sems can gyi mig gi rnam par
NK016(ma)013:1523: shes pa gnas su dag pa byang chub sems dpa'
NK016(ma)013:1524: sa'i snying po / 'gro ba rnams bla na med
NK016(ma)013:1525: pa'i gnas su skyed par mdzad pas phyag rgya rin
NK016(ma)013:1527: shar phyogs kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1528: don dam par sems can gyi mig gi yul gzugs
NK016(ma)013:1529: su snang ba gnas su dag pa badz+ra l+aa s+ya
NK016(ma)013:1530: ste / sku'i mchod pas mnyes par mdzad pa las
NK016(ma)013:1531: mi 'gyur bas phyag rgya rdo rje kha tshur can
NK016(ma)013:1532: ste / / rdo rje sgeg mo ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1534: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)013:1536: don dam par sems can gyi rna ba'i rnam par
NK016(ma)013:1537: shes pa gnas su dag pa byang chub sems dpa'
NK016(ma)013:1539: nyon mongs pa'i rgyun skad cig la gcod pas phyag rgya ral gri can /
NK016(ma)013:1540: lho phyogs kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi don
NK016(ma)013:1541: dam par sems can gyi sna'i yul drir snom pa
NK016(ma)013:1542: gnas su dag pa badz+ra m+aa le ste /
NK016(ma)013:1543: dri'i mchod pa rgyun mi chad par byed pas phyag rgya rin po che'i phreng ba can /
NK016(ma)013:1544: rdo rje phreng ba ma'i dbang tram +aa gar+b+ha ya /
NK016(ma)013:1545: tram m+aa le sa ma ya hoh a b+hi don
NK016(ma)013:1546: dam par sems can gyi sna'i rnam par shes pa
NK016(ma)013:1547: gnas su dag pa byang chub sems dpa' spyan ras
NK016(ma)013:1548: gzigs dbang phyug / nyon mongs pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pas phyag rgya pad+ma can /
NK016(ma)013:1549: nub phyogs kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi dbang
NK016(ma)013:1550: don dam par sems can gyi rna ba'i yul sgrar
NK016(ma)013:1551: grags pa gnas su dag pa badz+ra g+airti ste /
NK016(ma)013:1552: sgra'i mchod pas mnyes par byed pas phyag rgya pi wam can /
NK016(ma)013:1553: rdo rje sgra dbyangs ma'i dbang h+r+aim h+aa h+aum pad+ma pra da ma /
NK016(ma)013:1554: h+r+aim g+ai ti r+aa go ham /
NK016(ma)013:1555: a b+hi don dam par sems can gyi lce'i rnam
NK016(ma)013:1556: par shes pa gnas su dag pa byang chub sems
NK016(ma)013:1558: nyon mongs thams cad 'joms par byed pas phyag rgya rdo rje can /
NK016(ma)013:1559: byang phyogs kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi dbang
NK016(ma)013:1560: don dam par sems can gyi lce'i yul ro bro
NK016(ma)013:1561: ba gnas su dag pa badz+ra n+airti ste /
NK016(ma)013:1562: ro'i mchod pas mnyes par byed pas phyag rgya gar bsgyur can /
NK016(ma)013:1563: rdo rje gar bsgyur ma'i dbang dz+rim ku ru p+aa na /
NK016(ma)013:1564: am n+airti r+aa ga ya mye /
NK016(ma)013:1565: a b+hi don dam par sems can gyi mig gi
NK016(ma)013:1566: dbang po gnas su dag pa byang chub sems dpa'
NK016(ma)013:1567: byams pa / nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba las skyobs pas phyag rgya klu shing mgo lcog can /
NK016(ma)013:1568: shar lho'i mtshams kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi
NK016(ma)013:1569: don dam par sems can gyi dus 'das pa zhes
NK016(ma)013:1570: bya ba gnas su dag pa badz+ra d+h+au pe ste
NK016(ma)013:1571: / shangs kyi mchod pas mnyes par mdzad pas phyag rgya spos khang can /
NK016(ma)013:1572: rdo rje bdug pa ma'i dbang /
NK016(ma)013:1573: mee tri d+h+aa ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)013:1575: a b+hi don dam par sems can gyi rna ba'i
NK016(ma)013:1576: dbang po gnas su dag pa byang chub sems dpa'
NK016(ma)013:1577: sgrib pa rnam par sel ba /
NK016(ma)013:1578: nyon mongs pa chos nyid du mkhyen pas phyag rgya pusti can /
NK016(ma)013:1579: lho nub mtshams kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi
NK016(ma)013:1580: dbang don dam par sems can gyi dus da lta
NK016(ma)013:1581: zhes bya ba gnas su dag pa badz+ra push+pe ste
NK016(ma)013:1582: / sku'i mchod pas mnyes par mdzad pas phyag rgya me tog can /
NK016(ma)013:1583: rdo rje ma tog ma'i dbang th+l+him nis+sa ram b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)013:1585: a b+hi don dam par sems can gyi sna'i dbang
NK016(ma)013:1586: po gnas su dag pa byang chub sems dpa' kun
NK016(ma)013:1587: tu bzang po / nyon mongs pa gnas dus dag
NK016(ma)013:1588: pa las dgos 'dod re ba yid bzhin du skong
NK016(ma)013:1589: bas phyag rgya rin po che'i snye ma can /
NK016(ma)013:1590: nub byang mtshams kyi byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po /
NK016(ma)013:1591: nyon mongs pa gnas su dag pa las dgos 'dod
NK016(ma)013:1592: re ba yid bzhin du skong bas phyag rgya rin
NK016(ma)013:1594: nub byang mtshams kyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi
NK016(ma)013:1595: don dam par sems can gyi dus ma 'ongs pa
NK016(ma)013:1596: zhes bya ba gnas su dag pa badz+ra +aa lo
NK016(ma)013:1597: ke ste / spyan gyi mchod pas mnyes par mdzad pas phyag rgya mar me can /
NK016(ma)013:1598: rdo rje mar me ma'i dbang h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)013:1599: bam d+ai pa su gi r+ai /
NK016(ma)013:1600: a b+hi don dam par sems can gyi lce'i dbang
NK016(ma)013:1601: po gnas su dag pa byang chub sems dpa' 'jam
NK016(ma)013:1602: dpal / nyon mongs pa'i zug rngu mi mnga' bas
NK016(ma)013:1603: shin tu mdzes pas phyag rgya me tog ut+pala can
NK016(ma)013:1604: dpal / / byang shar mtshams kyi byang chub sems
NK016(ma)013:1605: dpa' rnams kyi don dam par sems can gyi dus
NK016(ma)013:1606: ma nges pa zhes bya ba gnas su dag pa
NK016(ma)013:1607: dpal / / badz+ra gan+d+he ste / ljags byugs pa'i
NK016(ma)013:1608: mchod pas mnyes par mdzad pas phyag rgya byugs pa
NK016(ma)013:1609: dpal / / badz+ra gan+d+he ste / can / rdo
NK016(ma)013:1610: rje dri chab ma'i dbang mum sh+r+ai am r+aa g+aa
NK016(ma)013:1611: dpal / / badz+ra gan+d+he ste / can / ya s+w+aa h+aa / hohgan+d+he tsit+ta /
NK016(ma)013:1612: a b+hi don dam par sems can gyi lha'i 'jig
NK016(ma)013:1613: rten du lta ba gnas su dag pa lha'i thub
NK016(ma)013:1614: pa ste / nyon mongs pa nga rgyal gnas su dag par mdzad pas phyag rgya bi pam can /
NK016(ma)013:1615: lha'i bcom ldan 'das kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK016(ma)013:1617: a b+hi don dam par sems can gyi lha ma
NK016(ma)013:1618: yin gyi 'jig rten du lta ba gnas su dag
NK016(ma)013:1619: pa lha ma yin gyi thub pa ste /
NK016(ma)013:1620: nyon mongs pa phrag dog gnas su dag par mdzad pas phyag rgya go cha can /
NK016(ma)013:1621: lha ma yin gyi bcom ldan 'das kyi dbang mu ne h+aum t+r+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)013:1622: a b+hi don dam par sem can gyi mi'i 'jig
NK016(ma)013:1623: rten du lta ba gnas su dag pa mi'i thub
NK016(ma)013:1624: pa ste / nyon mongs pa 'dod chags gnas su
NK016(ma)013:1625: dag par mdzad pas phyag rgya gseg shang par bu
NK016(ma)013:1626: pa ste / can / mi'i bcom ldan 'das kyi dbang mu ne srum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)013:1627: a b+hi don dam par sems can gyi byol song
NK016(ma)013:1628: gi 'jig rten du lta ba gnas su dag pa
NK016(ma)013:1629: byol song gi thub pa ste /
NK016(ma)013:1630: nyon mongs pa gti mug gnas su dag par mdzad pas phyag rgya glegs bam pusti can /
NK016(ma)013:1631: byol song gi bcom ldan 'das kyi dbang mu ne bram s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)013:1632: a b+hi don dam par sems can gyi yi dwags
NK016(ma)013:1633: kyi 'jig rten du lta ba gnas su dag pa
NK016(ma)013:1634: yi dwags kyi thub pa ste /
NK016(ma)013:1635: nyon mongs pa ser sna gnas su dag par mdzad pas phyag rgya rin po che'i sgrom bu can /
NK016(ma)013:1636: yi dwags kyi bcom ldan 'das kyi dbang mu ne k+sham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)013:1637: a b+hi don dam par sems can gyi dmyal ba'i
NK016(ma)013:1638: 'jig rten du lta ba gnas su dag pa dmyal

NK016(ma)013:1641: dmyal ba'i bcom ldan 'das kyi dbang mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK016(ma)013:1642: a b+hi don dam par sems can gyi lus kyi
NK016(ma)013:1643: rnam par shes pa gnas su dag pa khro bo
NK016(ma)013:1644: chen po gshin rje gshed po ste /
NK016(ma)013:1645: byams pa chen pos 'gro ba'i don zhe sdang tshar
NK016(ma)013:1646: gcod par mdzad pas phyag rgya n+ri mgo gdengs pa
NK016(ma)013:1647: can / shar sgo'i bdag po'i dbang don dam par
NK016(ma)013:1648: sems can gyi rtag par lta ba gnas su dag
NK016(ma)013:1649: pa badz+ra am ku sha ste /
NK016(ma)013:1650: 'khor ba'i nyon mongs pa thugs rjes 'dzin par byed pas phyag rgya lcags kyu can /

NK016(ma)013:1894: bsod nams 'di yis sogs kyis dge ba bsngo'o //
NK016(ma)013:1895: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa rnams las byang bzhin mthar 'byung bar bya'o //
NK016(ma)013:1896: rnal 'byor spyi khrus phan bde'i chu rgyun gyis //
NK016(ma)013:1897: mtshams med lnga sbyong thar pa'i sgo dbye ba'i //
NK016(ma)013:1898: thabs mchog na rag dong sprugs dbang chog gi //
NK016(ma)013:1899: mtshams sbyor bde chen lam bzang zhes bya 'di //
NK016(ma)013:1900: skyabs kun snying po gter chen bla ma yi //
NK016(ma)013:1901: zhabs zung gtsug nor bsten pa'i gsol 'debs pa //
NK016(ma)013:1902: gnyos btsun dge bsnyen mi 'gyur dpal sgron gyis //
NK016(ma)013:1903: rang mnyam kun la phan sems dag pas spel //
NK016(ma)013:1904: dge sgrub de yi bsod nams mthus //
NK016(ma)013:1905: mkha' mnyam 'gro dang lhan cig tu //
NK016(ma)013:1906: yang dag snying po'i don rtogs nas //
NK016(ma)013:1907: gzhan don rlabs chen spyod par shog /
NK016(ma)013:1908: de ltar zhi khro na raka dong sprugs kyi rtsa ba'i dbang chog la /
NK016(ma)013:1909: rje btsun mi 'gyur dpal sgron gyis mdzad pa'i mtshams
NK016(ma)013:1910: sbyor lhan thabs nyid 'jug bde bklag chog ma'i dbang
NK016(ma)013:1911: du gzhung dkyus su bsdebs par mdzad pa po ni
NK016(ma)013:1912: rgyal sras gzhan phan mtha' yas te /
NK016(ma)013:1913: da lta snga 'gyur bka' ma'i skor rnams phyogs gcig
NK016(ma)013:1914: tu bsdu ba'i skabs su slar yang yig rnying dang
NK016(ma)013:1915: phyag rgyun sogs la bstun te zhi ba mor dpyad
NK016(ma)013:1916: pa'i sgo nas zhus zhing dag par byed pa po
NK016(ma)013:1917: ni 'jigs bral ye shes rdo rje'o //
NK016(ma)013:1918: 'dis kyang bstan pa'i snying po mi nub dar zhing rgyas pa'i rgyur gyur cig /
